= Smidig 2009 Conference site

== Getting started

<code>
Check out the code from http://svn.smidig.no/smidig2009/
Install Ruby
gem install rails --version=2.3.2 
gem install sqlite3-ruby --version=1.2.3
rake gems:install
rake db:migrate
rake db:populate
ruby script/server
http://localhost:3000
</code>

== Running the tests

<code>
rake test
</code>

== Deploying new version to staging environment

<code>
svn commit
rake deploy:staging:update
(if database was changed) rake deploy:staging:migrate
</code>

== Setting up the staging environment from scratch

<code>
svn commit
rake deploy:staging:setup
rake deploy:staging:migrate
</code>
